olor: #ccc;">Jane Street and Tower Research</a>) trade on its Binance.com e=
xchange through their offshore affiliates, though there are not=C2=A0<em>ze=
ro=C2=A0</em>mentions of terrorist financing in the CFTC complaint.=C2=A0</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And similarly <a href=3D"https://link.mail.blo=
ombergbusiness.com/click/31711038.259416/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9maWxlcy=
9saXRpZ2F0aW9uL2NvbXBsYWludHMvMjAyMy9jb21wLXByMjAyMy0xMDEucGRm/607f07ceef4b=
