ryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; =
text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> binary=
 options or contracts for differences</a>. Either way it lives on abroad, b=
ut not in the US.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The SEC wins, an=
